-raqqa-province/3646230.html|title=Kurdish-Arab Forces in Syria Make Gains in Raqqa Province|work=[[Voice of America]]|first=Sirwan|last=Kajjo|date=21 December 2016}}</ref>\n* {{flag|United Kingdom}}<ref name=\"GB\">{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/25/operation-raqqa-british-raf-pilots-switch-bombing-raids-heart/|title=Operation Raqqa: British RAF pilots to switch bombing raids to 'the heart' of Isil|publisher=[[The Daily Telegraph]]|first=Steven|last=Swinford|date=25 December 2016|accessdate=16 January 2017|newspaper=The Telegraph}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Germany}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tagesschau.de/ausland/luftangriffe-syrien-aufklaerungsbilder-bundeswehr-101.html|title=Zivile Opfer in Syrien. Bundeswehr in verheerenden Luftschlag involviert|work=[[Tagesschau (Germany)]]|author1=Volkmar Kabisch|author2=Reiko Pinkert|language=German|date=29 March 2017|accessdate=29 March 2017}}</ref>\n{{flag|Iraqi Kurdistan}}<ref name=\"Peshmerga\">{{cite web|url=https://sofrep.com/77726/kurdistans-counter-terrorist-group-assault-taqba-dam-syria/|title=Did Kurdistan's Counter-Terrorist Group assault the Tabqa Dam in Syria? - SOFREP|date=23 March 2017|publisher=}}</ref>\n----\n'''[[Southern Raqqa offensive (June 2017)|Co-belligerents]]'''<br />{{flagicon image|Flag_of_Syria.svg}} [[Syria|Syrian Arab Republic]]<ref name=\"Reuters\">{{cite web | url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-army-idUSKBN1941QO | title=Syrian army advances west of Raqqa: Hezbollah military media unit | publisher=Reuters | date=13 June 2017 | accessdate=13 June 2017}}</ref><br />{{flag|Russia}}<ref name=\"Russia\">{{cite web|url=http://aranews.net/2017/02/russia-bombs-isis-positions-in-raqqa/|title=Russia bombs ISIS positions in Raqqa|first=Hozan|last=Mamo|publisher=[[ARA News]]|date=18 February 2017|accessdate=18 February 2017|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219004345/http://aranews.net/2017/02/russia-bombs-isis-positions-in-raqqa/|arc